\left(\sum_{i=1}^n x_i\right)^2=\sum_{i=1}^n \sum_{j=1}^n x_i x_j=\sum^{n}_{i=1}x_i^2+\sum^n_{i=1}\sum_{j=1,j\not=i}^n x_i x_j\ge \sum_{i=1}^n x_i^2
\left(\sum_{i=1}^n x_i\right)^2=\left(\sum_{i=1}^n 1\cdot x_i\right)^2\le n\cdot\sum_{i=1}^{n} x_i^2
